<br>
&quot;Cryton I need a heal fast.&quot;  the human warrior feared for his life as the hill giant found a taste for his blood.  The barbarian quickly met the warrior's needs placing him well on the better side of health. <br>
  <br>
<br>
The bard fumbled with her songs as an enraged cyclops pounded her.  Raising a pray to her gawd, Rallos Zek, as she neared her demise.  Again the song of sirens had her attacker's heart.   She fled the battle so near death that life was nearly a fanciful dream.  Her barbarian ally gave her all he could and she found herself on the border of safe levels of health. <br>
