  <br>
<br>
Turning on the Hill Giant the cyclops laid blows that stagger the minds of most warriors. <br>
 And when the hill giant fell dead, the cyclops returned to the bard's side to protect her against all that would do her harm.  She was his and he was hers.<br>
<br>
  <br>
<br>
